Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.22,0:01:08.54,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爽子お風呂入っちゃいなさいよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.95,0:01:09.81,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,はい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.95,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,お一　爽子　最近どうだ　学校は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.27,0:01:21.36,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,た　楽しいよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.54,0:01:27.22,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今までも聞いたら　楽しいとは言ってたけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.72,0:01:29.90,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目に見えてウキウキしてるわね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.37,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ウキウキしてる　な
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.35,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恋かしら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.84,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爽子　俺の爽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.98,0:01:42.57,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やだもう　お父さんったら　何やってんの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.24,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸せ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,こんに幸せを味わてしまうと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.04,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味を知らなかったことを忘れてしまいそう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.50,0:01:55.80,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,独り占め
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.70,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意味はよくわからないけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.55,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんだかとっても幸せ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.45,0:02:08.79,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私　いま　人生の幸せを全部使い果たしちゃってるのかも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.91,0:02:13.60,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ああ　でも　それでも嬉しいなあ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.61,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,えっ　嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.09,0:02:23.10,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉田だって　あの目の細い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.25,0:02:24.10,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そうそう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.30,0:02:27.20,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中学時代　手一つけらんなかったって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.82,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先生泣かすわ　クラスの男子全員殴るわ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:34.57,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたし　そんなんよりもっとすごいこといろいろやってんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あと　あたしの目はそこまで細くない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.06,0:02:40.44,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんでしょ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.05,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,見た目じゃなかったんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.36,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ねえ　中学で１００人斬りってすごすぎる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.48,0:02:49.16,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしを満足させられる男が１００人もいるか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.81,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いるんなら　つれてきな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.34,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,見定めてやったら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ったく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.18,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私の武勇伝はあんなもんじゃないのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ま　噂だからね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.68,0:03:02.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,それに　みんなが言うほど目細くないもん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.20,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あんたが思ってるより細いけどね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.82,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まったく　嘘ばっか　嘘ばっか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.72,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子の噂だって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.36,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,どう思う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.11,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出所どこだって聞いてんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.76,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出所は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.18,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,さ　貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.98,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,みんな言ってるよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.38,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子自分の地位あげるために
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.13,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風早や　吉田さんや　矢野さんを利用してるって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.70,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絶対ありえないって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.71,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でもでも　一応聞いてとく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.48,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そんでさ　そこのラ一メンが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さん　吉田さん　おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.66,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,お　おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.77,0:03:58.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう　貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.43,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ねえねえ　あたし　男子全員殴ったんだって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.35,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしはね　超男すきで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.94,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中学で　すでに１００人ぎりなんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.32,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　そうなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.68,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二人とも強いんだね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.66,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,シロ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:19.82,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉田さん　よかったら　これ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　何これ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.11,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中間テストの要点ノ一ト
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.88,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨夜作ってみたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.54,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もし　使えたらと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.74,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,pure white
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.72,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使わせていただきます
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.16,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの　矢野さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.27,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,え
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.47,0:04:43.78,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪談の練習用にビデオを借りに行こうと思うんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.53,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,よかったら　お勧めのビデオを教えてくれないかな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.50,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,pure whites
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.70,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,な　吉田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.98,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,それ　コヒ一させて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺も　束子やるからさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.29,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.58,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,えっ　いい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.03,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もちろん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.71,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.74,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人の役にたてるのはとても嬉しい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.28,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,triple pure whites
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.25,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,えっ　龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう　真田君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.01,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.19,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遅いなぁ　風早君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.16,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,お前信じてないな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.71,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺　ほんとに昨夜みたんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.24,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ちっちゃいおじさん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.95,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ピン　俺早く教室へ行きたいんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.83,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨夜　酒を飲んでいたら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.36,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おちょこの回りを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.52,0:05:43.37,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何人も何人もくるくる回ってて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.19,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,くるくる　くるくる　くるくる　くるくる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.41,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そのうこ一人ずつ　おちょこの中に入ってたんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.05,0:05:53.40,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ピン　俺　遅刻だっつってんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.28,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,うまくできてんだよ　あいつら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.07,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺　いくぞ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.02,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,で　どうなんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.41,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの黒沼って女子は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.70,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あっ　なんで黒沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.75,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あいつと目を会わせてから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.30,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,変なこと続きだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おまえ　となりだから　いろいろ知ってんだろう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.62,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あいつ　呪とか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.41,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺は自分で見た物を信じるよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.57,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺が見た黒沼は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.25,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前向きで　いい子だよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おまえ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.31,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黒沼とデキてんのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.82,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なに　はにかんでんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.66,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まさか　まじで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.71,0:06:35.45,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言うな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.16,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,それ以上はお前が言うな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.02,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺　もう行くかんな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.01,0:06:46.04,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,マ　マジ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.12,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兄役すぎね一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.95,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そんでそんで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.28,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.58,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.56,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遅かつたじゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.73,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ピンにちっちゃいおじさんの話聞かされてた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何それ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知らねー
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.44,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おでこ　出てる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.20,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,普通かなぁ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.16,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨日独り占めとかいっちゃったけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おでこ　や　やっばもっかい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.25,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,見たいな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,デキてんのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.26,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やっべ一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.76,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もう見れね一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.73,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　おでこが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.36,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,残念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.89,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸せを感じる毎日の中で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.72,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日に日に鼓動が高まっていく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.51,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皆はどう思ってるかな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.10,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私といて　楽しいかな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.56,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そうだといいなあ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.46,0:07:59.35,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そうだといいなあ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.31,0:08:06.81,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今まで周りに人がいないのが当然だと思ってきたから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.61,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.80,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そんなこと　考えたこともなかった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.49,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの日から
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.77,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今まで知らなかった気持ちばかりで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.30,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心がいっばい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.17,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大事にしたいな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.25,0:08:34.02,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,始めてもらったプレゼントみたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.78,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あっ　矢野さん　吉田さん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あのう　なんか　最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.70,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噂になってんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,はは　そうみたいだね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.45,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんか　どんどんすごくなってて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.66,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉田さん　お爺さんを倒して血まみれにしたって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.02,0:09:01.13,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,え　いや　転んだ爺さんを助け起こしたことならあるけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.51,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんは援交の斡旋してるって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.71,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やるか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.37,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もちろん　私たこは全然信じてないけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.65,0:09:15.43,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,その噂流してるのが黒沼さんだって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.92,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ありえない　絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.32,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんで急にそんな噂があって思うと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんか心配で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.59,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ちょっと　ひどいよね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.83,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あんな噂流すなんてさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.01,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本当信じられ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.14,0:09:35.15,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近前よりもっと恐れられてる気がする
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.42,0:09:39.60,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あっ　篠ちゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:42.77,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ちょっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.22,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あのさ　あんた最近すごい噂になってんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.57,0:09:55.54,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　霊感とか呪とかの噂　篠ちゃんも聞いたんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.75,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やっぱり誤解で　なかなかなくならないから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.97,0:10:02.89,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誤解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.93,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そうか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.49,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そうだよね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.15,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子が友達の悪口流すなんてありえないし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.58,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でも　それも前より気にならないってゆ一か
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.79,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周りの人たちもすごくよくしてくれて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.79,0:10:21.91,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんか柔らかい感じになったね　貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.77,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ううん　なんだって皆貞子貞子言ってんのかね一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.57,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,だから　悪目立ちするんでしょ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子もあたしらも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.73,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしらはあれだけどさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子のはいつもと違うタイブの噂じゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.96,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でもよかったね　友達できて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.47,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんと吉田さんだっけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.47,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,えっ　友達じゃないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.27,0:10:52.87,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　えっ　ああ　そうなの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.80,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.89,0:10:54.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待って　続きが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.05,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ちょうどいい　ちょっと来い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.89,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友達じゃないの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.30,0:11:07.33,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,うん　友達って矢野さん吉田さんの関係みたいな感じだよね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.33,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛いよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.29,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二人を見てるとね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.62,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,バカ力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.51,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,お互いすごく大好きなんだなぁって思うんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.85,0:11:18.76,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,たから　まだそこまではおこがましいってゆ一か
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.69,0:11:21.88,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,たけど　私は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.37,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二人のことが大好きだから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.65,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もし　そうなれる日がきたら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.90,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,すごくいいなあって思ってる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.31,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,は　野球部のマル日練習メニュ一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍に渡しとけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.46,0:11:44.78,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ふざけんな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.32,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,イテッ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.24,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ああ　なんかむかつく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.38,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,どいつもこいつも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.99,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,落ち着きな　チズ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.04,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友達じゃないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:11:58.79,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの言葉にどんな意味があんのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.60,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしらまだ貞子に何も聞いてないでしょ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:07.69,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,実際問題　あたしらが貞子と友達かっていったら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.74,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,それはそれで微妙じゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.33,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,﻿そうだね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.44,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あれ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.83,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,どうしたんだろう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.04,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いつも笑いあっている二人は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.38,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.11,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,こっちきて座って
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.47,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんか　元気ない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.49,0:12:36.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大事な話だからさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.59,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絶対嘘付かないで答えて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.69,0:12:45.09,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしは　あたしらは　あんたのことが好きだよ　貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.89,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あんたは
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.09,0:12:48.98,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,どう思ってる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.24,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしらのこと　好き
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.80,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好きっていうか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.57,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好きっていうよりも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.13,0:13:03.77,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.64,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.62,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,うん　分かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.59,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子　困らせたね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.90,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,こんなちょっとのことで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,気持ち分かってもらえたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.24,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そういうものなのかな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.64,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしらはあんたのことが好きだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.36,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凄く嬉しいはずなのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.92,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんと吉田さんの背中が
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.17,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やっぱり元気なくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.64,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんだか私まで悲しい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:51.40,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私に何か元気づけられることないかなぁ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.92,0:13:56.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,それで　調子に乗って　吉田と矢野もバックにつけてさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.91,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,バック
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.41,0:14:02.34,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,しかも　風早までいいように使って
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.48,0:14:03.67,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風早君も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.84,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なんか凄い人だな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まじで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.25,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あの貞子が
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.84,0:14:15.71,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いつのまにか貞子から裏番に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.49,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でもでも　矢野と吉田の黒い噂も凄いよね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黒い噂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.57,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私のバックについてる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.06,0:14:29.20,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　それで元気なかったんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.07,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傷ついてたんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.96,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子のせいだよね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そうそう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.26,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子が周りうろちょろするから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.30,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あ　風早もさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.95,0:14:44.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,このまま貞子につきまとわれたら　株落とすよ　絶対
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.01,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私のせい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.57,0:15:00.42,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんと吉田さんは　ただやさしくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.27,0:15:04.93,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,優しい気持こだけで　私にせっしてくれてるんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.39,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.17,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子が周りうろちょろするから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.13,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私がそばにいるせいで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.01,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周りの人傷つけてるの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.79,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私がそばにいると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.60,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんと吉田さんみたいに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.59,0:15:26.03,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風早君もいつか傷つけてしまうの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聞いたか　あちいちゃおじさんの話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.17,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,え　俺みたことあるよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.31,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺も見た
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.18,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まじで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,うん　扇子を作り
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.54,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘘　嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.81,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.17,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周りにいないほうがいいの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.41,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,周りにいちゃう　いけないの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.65,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何　そのまるで泣きはらしたような目は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.76,0:16:19.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野ちんこそ　まるで　徹夜でもしたみたい目してんじゃん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.49,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野ちん
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.48,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしらの噂　貞子が流したと思ってるの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正直　分かんなくなった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.60,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨日の貞子の答え聞いたら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.86,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少なくとも　貞子の中ではあたしらを好きじゃないんだからな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.43,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好きかって　聞き方したもんね　ちづ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.44,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好きって　即答してもらえたら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.55,0:17:03.14,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私たちのうわさなんか流すはずない　そう信じられるって思ったんでしょう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.14,0:17:10.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子が噂なんか流すわけないって　百パ一セント思ってたのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.27,0:17:15.97,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いまは　そうだったら　どうしようって思ってる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.73,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子が噂流すわけないって思いたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.80,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,そう思ってる自分がすごくいやだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.04,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.09,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,おはよう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.48,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目赤い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.79,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.27,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,私が元気なくさせてたんだね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.23,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,なに　それ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.72,0:17:53.68,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,見ちゃうだね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.87,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先行くね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.70,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ちょっ　貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.02,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝ってたよ　貞子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.06,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,元気なくさせてって　どういう意味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.18,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,まさか　本当に貞子が噂を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.21,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,やめて　やめてよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.21,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしだっていやだってば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もしかして昨日のこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.13,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好きじゃなくてごめんねってこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.67,0:18:23.77,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,どっちにしろきっついね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.51,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,うん　きつい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.34,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,うぬばれてたのかな　あたし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.78,0:18:33.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貞子にとって結構大きい存在だと思ってたんだよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.46,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしだって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.76,0:18:38.13,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確実に好かれてると思ってたってば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.77,0:18:41.80,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あたしが思ってたよりずっと傷ついてたんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.66,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんと吉田さんは
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.53,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噂してる人たち探して　誤解を解きたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.88,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢野さんと吉田さんは　バ一クについてるとかじゃなくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.52,0:18:57.47,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ただやさしいだけなんだよって　話したい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.37,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誤解なら私にも　とき方が分かるもの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.84,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でも　見つからない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.07,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噂してる人たち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.78,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いいか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.47,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早く戻ってほしいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.21,0:19:17.74,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いつもの元気な笑ってる矢野さんと吉田さんに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.22,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,いけない　いけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.25,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,泣きたいのは二人の方なのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.22,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黒沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.96,0:19:38.79,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待って
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.46,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺なんかした
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.61,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あのう　私用事があるので
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.40,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先泣いてた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.67,0:19:51.03,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺のこと避けてるみたいだし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,俺黒沼を傷つけるようなこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.54,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嫌われるようなこと何かやった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.93,0:19:58.95,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,あるなら言って
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,し　してない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.00,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風早君は何もしてないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:04.61,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.40,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.60,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,もしこの先何があつたとしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.85,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嫌うことなんて絶対にないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.23,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何があったって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.27,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絶対にないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.67,0:20:22.55,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黒沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.03,0:20:27.31,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,お前もうすぐテストだって余裕だな
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.67,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.59,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黒沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.83,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風早君　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.93,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何があっても風早君がずっと避けないって言ってくれたのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.83,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でも私がそばにいると迷惑になる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.90,0:20:48.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迷惑になる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.65,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でも　避けたくない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.63,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,離れたほうがいい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.56,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,でもそばにいたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.17,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,避げることは正しいの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.08,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,間違ってるの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.13,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,わかんないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.96,0:21:05.88,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,わかんない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.85,0:21:07.97,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,どうしたらいいのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.47,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,わかんないよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.75,0:22:27.34,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大切な人達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.92,0:22:30.66,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今私ができること
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.68,0:22:33.52,JP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,次回　決意
